WEBVTT

00:01:28.366 --> 00:01:30.467
Qanday his qilyapsiz? Rasvo?

00:01:30.491 --> 00:01:32.871
Yuvib tashlash uchun sovun kerakmi?

00:01:34.372 --> 00:01:35.986
Siz hozir shunday his qilyapsiz

00:01:36.010 --> 00:01:38.622
lekin kelajakda siz bunday his qilmaysiz.

00:01:39.454 --> 00:01:41.379
Ohirgi 100 yil davomida

00:01:41.403 --> 00:01:43.380
bizga yaqin turgan mikroskopik olam bilan

00:01:43.404 --> 00:01:46.019
hammamiz raqobatdosh munosabatda bo'ldik.

00:01:46.043 --> 00:01:48.165
Agar uyingizda parazit yoki 
rakovinangizda

00:01:48.189 --> 00:01:49.423
bakteriyalar bor desam,

00:01:49.447 --> 00:01:51.774
bunga inson yaratgan yechim bor, ya'ni

00:01:51.798 --> 00:01:54.934
bunday mavjudodlarni yo'q qiladigan

00:01:54.958 --> 00:01:56.251
vosita.

00:01:56.843 --> 00:02:00.718
Hozirgi kunda biz ko'plab mikroskopik 
mavjudodlarni yo'q qilishga kurashamiz.